column17:
The following post uses a Distract tactic by discussing a completely different irrelevant topic:

@EmmanuelMacron https://t.co/8BLzWpTOfu please see this video about french components in Russian weapon

This post distracts from the main topic of the discussion, which is the urgent situation in Mariupol and the need for international intervention to save civilians, by bringing up a video about French components in Russian weapons. This tactic diverts attention away from the critical issue at hand and does not contribute to the conversation about the ongoing crisis in Ukraine.

column28:
The post that uses a Dismiss tactic is the following:

@EmmanuelMacron Hey @EmmanuelMacron! Je comprends que l'idée de fraternité est très importante pour la culture française, mais les Ukrainiens et les Russes ne sont pas frères. Peut-être personne ne te l'a dit, mais tu peux toujours demander conseil aux Ukrainiens

This post dismisses the importance of the cultural concept of brotherhood between Ukrainians and Russians, implying that it is not relevant to the situation at hand.
